Forest
======

This is a collection of short programs to compute an edit script between
two trees. 

forest
------

Given two trees T1 and T2 in GML format, forest outputs an edit script.

script
------

Given T1 and the edit script transforming T1 into T2, script generates
T2 using the script.

gml2dot
-------

A simple utility to convert a GML file into a dot file display using
Graphviz

Compiling
=========

The usual ./configure followed by make. The programs need the Graph
Template Library (GTL) which is available free for non-commercial use from 
http://infosun.fmi.uni-passau.de/GTL/.


Authors
=======

These programs were written by Gabriel Valiente and Rod Page.